#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:5
msgid "3D Cursor"
msgstr "3D kursor"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:7
msgid ""
"The 3D Cursor is simply a point in 3D space which can be used for a "
"number of purposes."
msgstr ""
"3D kursor je ništa drugo do tačka u 3D prostoru, koju možemo upotrebiti "
"na različite načine."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:11
msgid "Placement"
msgstr "Pozicioniranje"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:13
msgid "There are a few methods to position the 3D cursor."
msgstr "3D kursor može se pozicionirati na nekoliko načina."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:17
msgid "Direct Placement with the Mouse"
msgstr "Direktno pozicioniranje mišem."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:22
msgid "Positioning the 3D cursor with two orthogonal views."
msgstr "Pozicioniranje 3D kursora pomoću dva pregleda u ortogonalnoj projekciji."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:24
msgid ""
"Using :kbd:`LMB` in the 3D View will place the 3D cursor directly under "
"your mouse pointer."
msgstr ""
"Koristeći :kbd:`LMB` u 3D prikazu postaviće 3D kursor direktno ispod "
"kursora miša."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:26
msgid ""
"For accuracy you should use two perpendicular orthogonal 3D Views, i.e. "
"any combination of top :kbd:`Numpad7`, front :kbd:`Numpad1` and side "
":kbd:`Numpad3`. That way you can control the positioning along two axes "
"in one view and determine depth in the second view."
msgstr ""
"Za precizno postavljanje 3D kursora, trebalo bi koristiti dva 3D prikaza "
"u ortogonalnoj projekciji, tj. bilo koju kombinaciju sa pogledom odozgo "
":kbd:`Numpad7`, spreda :kbd:`Numpad1` ili sa strane :kbd:`Numpad3`. "
"Ovako, u jednom prikazu pozicionirate 3D kursor u odnosu na dve ose, a u "
"drugom prikazu odredite poziciju na trećoj osi."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:30
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"By default the depth of the geometry under the cursor is used, this can "
"be disabled using the *Cursor Depth* toggle in the :doc:`Preferences "
"</editors/preferences/interface>`."
msgstr ""
"Kursor je klasično osetljiv na \"dubinu\"; ovo se može isključiti pomoću "
"*Cursor Depth* prekidača u :doc:`User Preferences "
"</preferences/interface>`."

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:35
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Snap Menu "
"</scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/snap>` which allows the "
"cursor placement relative to scene objects."
msgstr ""
"Meni prijanjanja :doc:`Snap Menu "
"</editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/snap>` koji omogućava "
"funkcije za pozicioniranje kursora u odnosu na objekte u sceni."

