#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:57
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Upotreba"

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/3d_cursor.rst:59
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The 3D Cursor is used as the origin for any added object, can be used and"
" moved with the :doc:`snap tool "
"</scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/snap>`, and is an option "
"for the :doc:`pivot point "
"</scene_layout/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/index>`."
msgstr ""
"3D Cursor se koristi kao centralna tačka za novokreirani objekat, može se"
" pomerati uz *prijanjanje* :doc:`snap tool "
"</editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/snap>`, a služi i kao "
"*tačka oslonca* :doc:`pivot point "
"</editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/control/pivot_point/index>`."

